00:16:21.000 --> 00:16:24.000
Mi'n gweld yna, Gardiant a News of the World.

00:16:24.000 --> 00:16:27.000
Ni'n gweld yna Gardiant i chi.

00:16:27.000 --> 00:16:29.000
A News of the World i chi.

00:16:29.000 --> 00:16:33.000
Oedd y Cymro i chi, oedd yr Herald o Wales i chi, a falle bod unedd o'i arall.

00:16:33.000 --> 00:16:41.000
